762
00:35:50,920 --> 00:35:53,550
So, what other things?

763
00:35:53,550 --> 00:35:56,761
There's one problem that runs
through this entire literature.

764
00:35:56,761 --> 00:35:57,260
OK.

765
00:35:57,260 --> 00:35:58,880
So here's the deal.

766
00:35:58,880 --> 00:36:03,380
You are a-- uh--
