768
00:36:06,685 --> 00:36:08,775
and you know all about
this handicap principle.

769
00:36:08,775 --> 00:36:12,170
And you know the fact that
big, dramatic secondary sexual

770
00:36:12,170 --> 00:36:14,640
characteristics on
guys is a marker

771
00:36:14,640 --> 00:36:17,440
of better immune systems
and more fertile sperm

772
00:36:17,440 --> 00:36:18,930
and all sorts of great stuff.

773
00:36:18,930 --> 00:36:22,270
So you go out of your way to
go and find one of those guys.

774
00:36:22,270 --> 00:36:23,620
You mate with him.

775
00:36:23,620 --> 00:36:26,090
And you've just given birth.

776
00:36:26,090 --> 00:36:30,290
So, knowing what you know, what
