818
00:38:23,360 --> 00:38:26,390
where the magic does not occur.

819
00:38:26,390 --> 00:38:28,080
There is no chemistry
between them.

820
00:38:28,080 --> 00:38:30,090
The female rejects the guy.

821
00:38:30,090 --> 00:38:33,880
And, at that point, what he
does is, in the next round,

822
00:38:33,880 --> 00:38:37,560
